data.description: Motivated Sellers! This home is priced to sell. Come and experience this better than new 4bdrm/3.5bath home! Not even two years old! The spacious design of this home gives you ample room to stretch out & enjoy the many spaces. The beautiful gourmet kitchen includes granite countertops, double oven, gas cooktop, upgraded dishwasher, upgraded sink faucet, & huge pantry. The dining rm is expansive allowing for a 10+ person table. The living rm is spacious & has a beautiful rustic wood mantle installed over the tile fireplace, giving it a cozy feel. The main level boasts all LVP flooring and the main level half bath has been recently renovated. Blinds throughout the whole home as well as lighting throughout most of the home has been upgraded.  The home office rounds out the main level. As you head upstairs you enter the spacious loft area.  The homeowner’s suite boasts a luxurious ensuite 5-piece bath & two walk-in closets. There are three add’l bdrms upstairs, two of them with walk-in closets. Two of the bdrms share a Jack & Jill bath with their own sinks. Plus, a 3rd hallway bath upstairs. The laundry room upstairs makes life easier. The basement is bright with light and is a walk out with 9’ ceilings. Basement is plumbed for a bath and ready to finish as needed. The oversized 3-car garage with beautiful epoxy flooring has been insulated, painted, and add'l outlets added in 2023.  As you head out to the deck off the kitchen, you enjoy views from up high and a fully landscaped backyard. Concrete patio has been extended for addtl entertaining area. Natural gas line was added to the deck to grill at your convenience. Ring camera for extra security. So many upgrades with this one and ready for you to move in! Great location with south facing driveway for excellent snowmelt in the winter.  Amazing neighborhood with trails, a community pool, playgrounds, open space, and so much more to come!
